      • createForTrackSelector

        public static TrackSelectionDialog createForTrackSelector(com.google.android.exoplayer2.trackselection.DefaultTrackSelector trackSelector,
                                                          android.content.DialogInterface.OnDismissListener onDismissListener)
        Creates a dialog for a given DefaultTrackSelector, whose parameters will be automatically updated when tracks are selected.
        パラメータ:
        trackSelector - The DefaultTrackSelector.
        onDismissListener - A DialogInterface.OnDismissListener to call when the dialog is dismissed.

      • createForMappedTrackInfoAndParameters

        public static TrackSelectionDialog createForMappedTrackInfoAndParameters(int titleId,
                                                                         com.google.android.exoplayer2.trackselection.MappingTrackSelector.MappedTrackInfo mappedTrackInfo,
                                                                         com.google.android.exoplayer2.trackselection.DefaultTrackSelector.Parameters initialParameters,
                                                                         boolean allowAdaptiveSelections,
                                                                         boolean allowMultipleOverrides,
                                                                         android.content.DialogInterface.OnClickListener onClickListener,
                                                                         android.content.DialogInterface.OnDismissListener onDismissListener)
        Creates a dialog for given MappingTrackSelector.MappedTrackInfo and DefaultTrackSelector.Parameters.
        パラメータ:
        titleId - The resource id of the dialog title.
        mappedTrackInfo - The MappingTrackSelector.MappedTrackInfo to display.
        initialParameters - The DefaultTrackSelector.Parameters describing the initial track selection.
        allowAdaptiveSelections - Whether adaptive selections (consisting of more than one track) can be made.
        allowMultipleOverrides - Whether tracks from multiple track groups can be selected.
        onClickListener - DialogInterface.OnClickListener called when tracks are selected.
        onDismissListener - DialogInterface.OnDismissListener called when the dialog is dismissed.

      • getOverrides

        public java.util.List<com.google.android.exoplayer2.trackselection.DefaultTrackSelector.SelectionOverride> getOverrides(int rendererIndex)
        Returns the list of selected track selection overrides for the specified renderer. There will be at most one override for each track group.
        パラメータ:
        rendererIndex - Renderer index.
        戻り値:
        The list of track selection overrides for this renderer.
